(OOC:Forget what I said before Code. I'e been reding your posts wrong 
sometimes. My fault. Sorry.)

Starscream looked around. A sorry bunch of Predacons lost in the 
wilderness. He looked at everyone. Drilbit, Atma, Pseudo, Phobia, 
himself.

"All right, 5 of us. We each vote. Can't vote for yourselves. I gotta 
put my vote towards Phobia. He saved our butts back at the cave, and 
he was willing to sacrifice himself to save us all. I think he'd have 
the courage and guts to make a leader."
